    settings_bg_code: 'Animated background (code)', settings_bg_code_hint: 'Build your own animated background in JavaScript — it runs in an isolated sandbox', settings_bg_code_name: 'Name', settings_bg_code_templates: 'Starter templates', settings_bg_code_tpl_stars: 'Stars', settings_bg_code_tpl_waves: 'Waves', settings_bg_code_tpl_grid: 'Neon dots', settings_bg_code_tpl_nebula: 'Nebula', settings_bg_code_tpl_aurora: 'Aurora', settings_bg_code_tpl_matrix: 'Matrix', settings_bg_code_tpl_confetti: 'Confetti', settings_bg_code_tpl_orbit: 'Orbits', settings_bg_code_tpl_plasma: 'Plasma', settings_bg_code_ai_hint: 'No coding needed: pick a template below, paste a shared background, or just ask Xenon — e.g. "create an animated background with blue particles drifting".', settings_bg_code_import: 'Import background', settings_bg_code_export: 'Export background', settings_bg_code_help_title: 'How to write the code', settings_bg_code_help_contract: 'Define a function draw(ctx, t, w, h): ctx is the canvas 2D context, t the elapsed seconds, w and h the size in pixels. It is called about 60 times a second to paint one frame. Declare any particles or state with const/let above the function so they persist between frames.', settings_bg_code_help_can: 'You can use the whole canvas 2D API, Math and Date.', settings_bg_code_help_cant: 'The sandbox blocks network, dashboard, files and settings access: a background, even an imported one, can do nothing harmful.', settings_bg_code_editor: 'Code', settings_bg_code_editor_hint: 'for those who want to write it by hand', settings_bg_code_replace: 'Replace the current code with this template?', dlg_cancel: 'Cancel', dlg_save: 'Save', dlg_replace: 'Replace', settings_bg_code_error: 'Code error', settings_bg_code_nodraw: 'Define a function draw(ctx, t, w, h).', settings_bg_code_note: 'The code paints a full-screen canvas and runs in an isolated sandbox: no network, no access to the dashboard, your files or your settings. Contract: define function draw(ctx, t, w, h) — ctx is the 2D context, t the elapsed seconds, w and h the size in pixels. Only import backgrounds from people you trust.',
