    settings_sdk_enable: 'Enable third-party widgets',
    settings_sdk_enable_hint: 'add the "Custom widget" tile from the "+" palette and pick a package',
    settings_sdk_note: 'A widget cannot touch the server, your files or your settings: it runs in an isolated sandbox with no internet access, and can only see the data you approve and run the actions you allow (media keys, volume, mic mute, lighting, open a link) — each re-checked by the server. Every package asks you for permissions before it appears.',
